Leave the diningtable. Turn right. Enter the diningtable. Turn right. Approach the diningtable.

Put the bread on the diningtable.

Pick up the bread from the table.

Put the bread on the diningtable.

Pick up bread from the bed.
Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the dining table on your right.
Place bread on the dining table.

Pick up bread from the bed.
Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the dining table on your right.
